v11:
 * shorter line for an error
v9
 * Fix an indexing logic error in amd_hfi_fill_metadata() leading to wrong
   APIC IDs being used.
 * Add a missing space
 * use dev_err/dev_warn
 * pcct->PCCT
 * signed->unsigned
v3:
 * Reverse xmas tree order in amd_hfi_fill_metadata()
 * s,for_each_present_cpu,for_each_possible_cpu,
v2:
 * Drop __packed
